      • Route

        public Route(java.lang.String airline,
             java.lang.String sourceAirport,
             java.lang.String destinationAirport,
             java.lang.Boolean codeShare,
             int stops,
             java.util.ArrayList<java.lang.String> equipment)
        Constructor for route class.
        Parameters:
        airline - 2-letter (IATA) or 3-letter (ICAO) code of the airline
        sourceAirport - 3-letter (IATA) or 4-letter (ICAO) code of the source airport
        destinationAirport - 3-letter (IATA) or 4-letter (ICAO) code of the destination airport
        codeShare - "Y" if this flight is a codeshare (that is, not operated by Airline, but another carrier), empty otherwise
        stops - Number of stops on this flight ("0" for direct)
        equipment - 3-letter codes for plane type(s) generally used on this flight
